HEADWORD: Makeweight
<hw>Make"weight`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which is
thrown into a scale to make weight; something of little account added to
supply a deficiency or fill a gap.</def>⟦br⟧
